A tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu cikin sauri a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai.
Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin EU / EU Economic Area da Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa cutar ta COVID-19 ta duniya tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, duk da cewa ta bambanta a ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai zurfi suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don kula da lafiyarsu, musamman ma yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai zurfi.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wasu cututtukan sambab da ba a san dalilin su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ce ke haifar da cutar, wanda ake kira da cutar coronavirus mai saurin kamuwa da cuta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an sake masa suna da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, kamuwa da numfashi tare da kumburi ko kuma ba tare da kumburi ba, kuma mafi yawansu suna murmurewa.
Kashi 14% na masu cutar kansa suna ci gaba zuwa mafi munin COVID-19 wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, kuma sauran kashi 6% na masu cutar suna fuskantar mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mai ƙarfi.
Kashi 4% na marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sun mutu saboda COVID-19.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya (UK) tare da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya
COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa daga China zuwa wasu yankuna na duniya, kuma cutar ta COVID-19 ta kasance ta fi yawa a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Spiteri et al., a cikin Eurosurveillance 2020, wanda aka buga a ranar 5 ga Maris, sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da shari'o'in COVID-19 na Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, Faransa ce ta fara bayar da rahoton mutane uku da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, wadanda suka fito daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu sabbin cututtukan COVID-19 a duk kasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, tare da samun mutum 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutuwar mutane 1,727 daga 31 ga Disamba, 2020, wanda 17,750 daga cikinsu da kuma mutuwar mutane 1,441 sun fito ne daga Italiya kadai.
Sanin jimillar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan abin da ya faru
Bayanai na lambobin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta duniya, kamar yadda Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) ta bayyana, ana samun su ne kawai daga tushen hukuma kamar su ofisoshin ma'aikatar lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da WHO, wanda ke sabuntawa kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da Italiya.
A matsayin wakilin adadin masu cutar COVID-19, mun sanya adadin COVID-19 a matsayin babban abin da ya faru na kwanaki 14, saboda haka muna la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya daga Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Bugu da kari, mun kwatanta adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a kowace kasa har zuwa karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da na Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya
Yanayin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya a cikin kwanaki 14 na jimlar lokaci an bi shi a lardin Hubei (China) gaba ɗaya (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya, adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (kayan aiki).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga karuwar gaggawa a cikin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma, sauran ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a cikin adadin COVID-19 (kayan aiki).
