Alamar farko da ta fi dacewa ta COVID-19 ita ce zazzabi, wanda zai iya bayyana ba tare da wani abu ba ko kuma tare da wasu alamun kamar tari mai bushe, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka, kumburi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, ciwon kirji, tashin hankali da kumburi.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna da matsalar numfashi da kuma/ko kuma rashin iskar oxygen a cikin jini tun daga ranar da suka kamu da cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, marasa lafiya suna iya fara nuna ciwon numfashi mai tsanani, rashin lafiyar jiki, ciwon acidic acid, da kuma coagulopathy.
"Masu fama da zazzabi da/ko cututtukan numfashi da kuma zazzabi mai tsanani, ko da ba su da wata matsala a binciken daukar hoto na huhu, ya kamata a fara gwada su don gano cutar.
Wani binciken da aka gudanar a karshen watan Disamba na shekarar 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98% na masu fama da cutar sun kamu da kumburi, kashi 76% sun kamu da tari, kashi 55% sun kamu da numfashi, kuma kashi 3% sun kamu da tari, kuma kashi 8% na marasa lafiya sun bukaci taimakon na'urar numfashi.
Kwanan nan, an sami irin wannan binciken a cikin ƙungiyoyin iyali biyu da kuma a cikin ƙungiyar da ke kamuwa da cutar daga wani mutum wanda ba shi da alamun cutar.
Idan aka kwatanta, binciken da aka yi a shekarar 2012 ya nuna cewa manyan alamun cutar na masu cutar MERS-CoV sune zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushe (47%) da kuma rashin numfashi (55%).
Koyaya, kashi 80% na masu cutar COVID-19 sun fi buƙatar na'urar numfashi, saboda yawan mutuwar MERS ya fi na COVID-19.
An kuma lura da ciwon hanci (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya na MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiya na SARS, zazzabi (99% - 100%), tari mai bushe (29% - 75%), rashin numfashi (40% - 42%), tari (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) sune manyan abubuwan da suka faru; kuma 14% - 20% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon numfashi.
