Cutar ta gama gari sau da yawa tana faruwa a cikin iyali ɗaya ko a cikin rukuni ɗaya ko a cikin abin hawa, kamar jirgin ruwa mai nishaɗi.
Yawancin marasa lafiya suna da tarihin tafiya ko zama a cikin ruwa ko wasu yankuna da ke fama da cutar a cikin makonni biyu kafin cutar ta bayyana, ko kuma sun kasance tare da mutane ko marasa lafiya da ke da cutar.
Amma, rahotanni sun nuna cewa mutane na iya ɗaukar kwayar cutar sama da makonni biyu ba tare da nuna alamun cutar ba, kuma masu lafiya da suka tsira daga asibiti na iya sake ɗaukar kwayar cutar, wanda hakan zai ba da gargadi don tsawaita lokacin keɓewa.
A farkon wannan ciwon, marasa lafiya suna da ƙarancin adadin farin jini (musamman lymphocytes).
Misali, an gano lymphophenia tare da ƙididdigar farin jini; 4×109/L; gami da ƙididdigar lymphocytes; 1×109/L mafi girman adadin aspartate aminotransferase da Virimiya 1,099 a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
A wasu marasa lafiya, an sami karuwar ƙwayar hanta da ƙwayar tsoka da kuma ƙwayar myoglobin a cikin jini, kuma an sami karuwar furotin mai aiki da C da kuma ƙarancin erythrocytes a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya.
A cikin marasa lafiya masu tsananin rashin lafiya, yawan D-dimer, wanda shine samfurin rage fibrin, yana ƙaruwa a cikin jini kuma yawan ƙwayoyin jini masu ƙwayoyin cuta yana raguwa.
Sakamakon radiography na kirji a yawancin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ya nuna rashin lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa akwai kumburi a bangarorin biyu ko kuma wani abu mai kumburi a cikin huhu.
Marasa lafiya sukan sha fama da ciwon huhu na yau da kullum, ciwon huhu mai tsanani, da kuma ciwon numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS).
ARDS yana sa mutum ya yi kumburi, ya yi ruwa, kuma ya yi ciwo mai yawa, kuma hakan yana sa iska ta yi sanyi sosai.
Kwayoyin alveoli na nau'i na I da na II suna rage yawan sinadarin lipid da furotin, suna ƙara damuwa, suna sa huhu su yi tsami, kuma suna ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da huhu.
